      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver, though it clearly shows its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading in the paint on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows significant wear, and the dashboard has a small crack from sun exposure. Mechanically, the car runs well and has been regularly maintained, though it may require some minor repairs or part replacements in the near future.",
