      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable condition, having been maintained to the most exacting standards. Every surface and mechanical component reflects a level of preservation typically reserved for private collections. We invite discerning buyers to experience a machine that transcends the standard pre-owned market. This is, without reservation, a definitive example of automotive excellence.",
