    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem! It has been pampered since day one and is in truly incredible, like-new condition inside and out. It\u2019s a total dream to drive and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I'm only selling it to make some space, but I know the next owner is going to be over the moon with it. Come check it out and see for yourself\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
