    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3 in collector-quality condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with double VANOS, delivering linear power to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and comprehensive subframe reinforcement. The chassis is dialed in with Bilstein PSS10 coilovers, while the factory limited-slip differential ensures optimal torque distribution. Zero oxidation, original paint depth, and a pristine interior make this a definitive driver\u2019s car for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
