    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle represents the pinnacle of pride-of-ownership. Presented in a breathtaking showroom finish, the exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like gloss with zero swirl marks, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. There are no rock chips, door dings, or blemishes to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather seats show no bolster wear, the original floor mats are pristine, and the interior still carries that distinct factory aroma. Mechanically, this car is flawless. It has been strictly garage-kept and maintained with an open-checkbook policy at authorized service centers\u2014all records are organized and available for review. With brand-new performance tires and a smooth, responsive drivetrain, this is a rare opportunity to own a truly immaculate example that drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership.",
      "price": 46500.0,
